</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BAE36CF6B2CFFBBFB3A7D2CF9A48DA2" blockId="0.[1258,2137,996,1304]" pageId="0" pageNumber="528">• Shoreward of the continental shelf, mostly shallow waters less than 180 m deep; two species occur in deep, oceanic waters (hundreds to thousands of meters deep), and two in rivers.</paragraph>
